<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: armor piercing shell -->
  <DMSE_Bullet_Dawnblade_Striker.label>穿甲砲彈</DMSE_Bullet_Dawnblade_Striker.label>
  
  <!-- EN: APT shell -->
  <DMSE_Bullet_Vulcan_WingBack.label>APT 砲彈</DMSE_Bullet_Vulcan_WingBack.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Type 85 Multi-Purpose-Quick-Firing System -->
  <DMSE_Gun_Dawnblade_Striker.label>85 型多用途速射系統</DMSE_Gun_Dawnblade_Striker.label>
  <!-- EN: An automated artillery system widely used on small to medium-sized frigates and corvettes in colonial fleets. -->
  <DMSE_Gun_Dawnblade_Striker.description>一種廣泛裝備於殖民艦隊中小型巡防艦與護衛艦的艦載多用途速射炮系統。</DMSE_Gun_Dawnblade_Striker.description>
  <!-- EN: Type 85 Multi-Purpose-Quick-Firing System -->
  <DMSE_Gun_Dawnblade_Striker.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>85 型多用途速射系統</DMSE_Gun_Dawnblade_Striker.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>
  
  <!-- EN: GAU-4 “Wing-Back” -->
  <DMSE_Gun_Vulcan_WingBack.label>GAU-4「翼衛」</DMSE_Gun_Vulcan_WingBack.label>
  <!-- EN: This is a gravship-based variant of the GAU-4 rotary cannon, also utilizing 20x102mm NATO ammunition. The ship-mounted turret features a longer barrel to increase effective range, but it also introduces a larger blind spot for close-range engagements. -->
  <DMSE_Gun_Vulcan_WingBack.description>這是 GAU-4 旋轉機炮的重力船搭載型，採用更長槍管以提升有效射程，但也帶來近距離交戰盲區較大的缺點。</DMSE_Gun_Vulcan_WingBack.description>
  <!-- EN: GAU-4 “Wing-Back” -->
  <DMSE_Gun_Vulcan_WingBack.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>GAU-4「翼衛」</DMSE_Gun_Vulcan_WingBack.verbs.Verb_Shoot.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Dawnblade "Striker" -->
  <DMSE_Turret_Dawnblade_Striker.label>MPQFS-85「前鋒」</DMSE_Turret_Dawnblade_Striker.label>
  <!-- EN: MPQFS-85 "Dawnblade" is an onboard multirole quick-firing cannon system. It uses drum magazines and an automatic revolver loader to permit a high rate of sustained fire.\n\nThe armor plating has been removed to allow emplacement to be redeployed as needed for heavy fire support. -->
  <DMSE_Turret_Dawnblade_Striker.description>MPQFS-85「前鋒」是一種殖民艦隊海軍常用的艦載多用途速射炮系統。它使用鼓式彈艙與自動左輪裝填機構，可維持高持續射速。</DMSE_Turret_Dawnblade_Striker.description>
  <!-- EN: Barrel durability -->
  <DMSE_Turret_Dawnblade_Striker.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelGizmoLabel>槍管耐久度</DMSE_Turret_Dawnblade_Striker.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelGizmoLabel>
  <!-- EN: Shots until barrel change -->
  <DMSE_Turret_Dawnblade_Striker.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelLabel>距離更換槍管剩餘射擊次數</DMSE_Turret_Dawnblade_Striker.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelLabel>
  <!-- EN: Cannot fire: Needs new reinforced barrel. -->
  <DMSE_Turret_Dawnblade_Striker.comps.CompRefuelable.outOfFuelMessage>無法開火：需要新的強化槍管。</DMSE_Turret_Dawnblade_Striker.comps.CompRefuelable.outOfFuelMessage>
  
  <!-- EN: GAU-4 “Wing-Back” -->
  <DMSE_Turret_Vulcan_WingBack.label>GAU-4「翼衛」</DMSE_Turret_Vulcan_WingBack.label>
  <!-- EN: This is a gravship-based variant of the GAU-4 rotary cannon, also utilizing 20x102mm NATO ammunition. The ship-mounted turret features a longer barrel to increase effective range, but it also introduces a larger blind spot for close-range engagements. -->
  <DMSE_Turret_Vulcan_WingBack.description>這是 GAU-4 旋轉機炮的重力船搭載型，炮塔採用更長槍管以提升有效射程，但也帶來近距離交戰盲區較大的缺點。</DMSE_Turret_Vulcan_WingBack.description>
  <!-- EN: Barrel durability -->
  <DMSE_Turret_Vulcan_WingBack.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelGizmoLabel>槍管耐久度</DMSE_Turret_Vulcan_WingBack.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelGizmoLabel>
  <!-- EN: Shots until barrel change -->
  <DMSE_Turret_Vulcan_WingBack.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelLabel>距離更換槍管剩餘射擊次數</DMSE_Turret_Vulcan_WingBack.comps.CompRefuelable.fuelLabel>
  <!-- EN: Cannot shoot: Needs new reinforced barrel. -->
  <DMSE_Turret_Vulcan_WingBack.comps.CompRefuelable.outOfFuelMessage>無法射擊：需要新的強化槍管。</DMSE_Turret_Vulcan_WingBack.comps.CompRefuelable.outOfFuelMessage>
  
